Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] What?! You were\Nplaying WIXOSS until four AM?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah, I showed it to\Nmy Grandma, and she got hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The deal was, loser had to\Npeel tangerines, and I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Now my hands are\Nall orange. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ewww!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--[RUKO yawns]\N--[YUZUKI] Yeesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,There's this stuff\Ncalled "soap"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,So you were saying we don't need\Nto battle each other anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The world can make\Nroom for one more Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Both of us can have\Nour wishes come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I don't have one.\NI haven't even thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--[KAZUKI] Let's go!\N--Hey, wait up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Finding other Selectors\Nis a real pain in the butt,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,not to mention exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean there\Naren't too many?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Or at least it\Nseems like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,since there's no\Neasy way to find 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? Tell 'er, Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. But LRIGs are\Nattracted to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We can identify\NSelectors on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Right over there for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Iona Urazoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What about her?\NIs she a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She's on TV a lot. Even\Nhad a new single jus' drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] The girl next\Nto her is one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Really? She's in\Nmagazines a lot too, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. It's\Non the tip of my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look it says here\Nshe goes to Gochu High!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Which high\Nschool? Say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[students murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Uh...\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Maybe this\Nisn't the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] C'mon, better\Nnow than never!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But I get first\Ndibs, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll set up matches for\Nafter-school and--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's her! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like the pictures...\NShe's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!\NLet's go challenge her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] Wait! Akira, please!\NI'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to battle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL] Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...a Selector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You're... Selectors too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are these\Nlosers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's too busy to sign\Nautographs right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,So buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhh! No. Wait. I just want--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:03:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for being my fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] If you want\Nsomething autographed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,then let's go someplace\Nprivate! You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--? Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] C'mon, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's too\Nnice to her fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Here! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,With all these\NSelectors, I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Or as I like to\Nsay: "Aki-lucky"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,So let's get a battle done\Nbefore class starts, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Which one of you\Ngirls is up first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] I-I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] All righty then.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! My name is Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:44.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Love it! Now let's get\Nthis party started, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,One nice and friendly\Nbattle ready to: Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] I assume you\Nboth are wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,what you're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,When a battlefield is\Nopened, any Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,candidates nearby\Nare drawn inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Well that's lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,--[TAMA meowing]\N--Wait! That sounds like...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--[TAMA squeals]\N--Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're gonna get\Nmy hair all goofed up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:36.92,Main,,0,0,0,,if you keep doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, it's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm first. Guess\Nit's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go: Battle Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Midoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,My LRIG is\NAki-lucky, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Meet Piriluk! Go\Nstompy-stompy on them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] A green deck\Nversus a blue deck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility\Nthis Hitoe girl may have
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw! Energy charge,\NMidoriko! Now Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,First up: Summon Sparrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparrow! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Whoa! She's\Nstarting off strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is\Nkeep Midoriko growing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.18,Main,,0,0,0,,so we don't\Nlose momentum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, what a meanie!\NWhatever shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You got this, Piriluk, just\NGrow and we'll take her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] But those green\Ndecks really are unnerving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what\Ncards Little Miss Four-Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,has in her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,To make things less scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just have her\Nthrow one of those cards away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] All right, Hitoe, I'm\Ngonna choose one of your cards
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,at random. Hope it's one you\Ncan afford to play without!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell: Too Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, not looking. Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm bettin' that's a\NLevel 3 card, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Expose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Bullseye!\NAki-lucky guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The card just vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's one of the blue\Ndeck's top strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A player can force their\Nopponent to lose a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Piriluk, Grow!\NAnd while you're at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,freeze Hitoe's Sparrow!\NClip its wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Aww, your cute little\Nbirdy's been put on ice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.95,Main,,0,0,0,,'til the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Midoriko...\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I only have two cards\Nleft! If I mess up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Just calm\Ndown, Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,If that's already\Ngotcha freakin' out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,wait 'til you see the other\Nstuff I've got in store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Piriluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Arts. Peeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Seen this\None? Super handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I pick a level,\Nthen you throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,all your cards that match it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,All... my cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what\NI should pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Level... two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad!\NShe can read her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:14.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Four...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,All Level Four cards:\NGo buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Jeez,\Npull it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Not that you\Nhave any hope of winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,but now you got me\Nwondering why
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,you want to become\Nan Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's find out your\Nlittle wish, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK] The poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK] She has no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, nobody wuvs Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,--[MIDORIKO] Hitoe! Come on!\N--She doesn't have any fwiends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We're still in this, so ignore\Nher and don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HITOE sobs quietly]\N--[AKIRA] Loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, what--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna put a stop\Nto her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll interfere\Njust like Kazuki did
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,when you and I\Nhad our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That should do the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki didn't stop the\Nbattle the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,it was the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,And that was only because\Nof an irregular occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,An interruption by someone who\Nknew nothing about the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Also... if ever a battle\Nis stopped on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,a huge penalty\Nis issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,A penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What about one for the way\NAkira's been playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She hasn't broken\Nany rules thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang. This game...\Nit's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] How could she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA meowing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Piriluk?\NFinish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I... don't have any\NLife Cloth left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't give\Nup now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Take guard against\Nthe attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? I'm just gonna lose\Nanyway. What's the use?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] Believe\Nin me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] The game's over.\NAkira won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried, but... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko begged me to\Nfight, but I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And now she's the\None paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,So. Who wants\Nto battle next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:41.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Already, Piriluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Crud. She falls\Nasleep so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, then. We'll just\Nhave to battle tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay? Can I get\Nyour cell number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you see... I\Ndon't have a cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No way, that is\Nso old school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta go! We're super\Nlate for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI & YUZUKI gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] I am not letting you go\Nuntil you give up the digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[school bells chiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,D'ja get in trouble\Nfor being tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah. But I just had\Nto stand out in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It was math class so\NI was lucky, or, sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, "Aki-lucky"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Oh God, make me cringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn. Akira's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,She'd probably thrash me as\Nhard as that other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, why did you give her\Nyour phone number then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What choice did I have?!\NShe wasn't gonna let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hey, I could battle\NAkira if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't agree\Nto a battle, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I was watching from the\Noutside. And you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, but that Hitoe\Ngirl wasn't bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know all the\NEternal Girl candidates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,would be this tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder... if I\Ncan win at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure you can! I mean, all you\Nneed to do is update your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But that means we'd have\Nto go to the card shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Umm... Yeah, unless\Nthat's a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I've never been\Nto one before! Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, we'll all\Ngo together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Whoa. I never knew\Nthere was a card shop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,in this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Kazuki, you're really\Nan expert on all this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was playing WIXOSS\Nbefore it got popular
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,When I recommended it to Yuzuki,\Nher deck had Hanayo in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Uh... Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:09.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wow. This place takes\Ncards pretty seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Huuuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP KEEP] Hey! Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We just got a new\NWIXOSS set in today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,And Yuzuki tagged\Nalong too! Been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,We're hoping to update\NYuzuki's deck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you mind giving\Nus some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,'Course not! You know I'd do\Nanything for you, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what you\Nneed and I'm all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI groans softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP KEEP] Let's see, Yuzuki's\Ndeck is Red Ambition, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, it should cycle a\Nlot better with an Adamasphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I think I've\Nheard of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a SIGNI from the\Nnew series, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP KEEP] Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's aren't any singles\Non the collector's market yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,All these packs\Nand nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What about these cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah. They won't really mesh well\Nwith the rest of Yuzuki's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't want\Nthis one, do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I could have it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Well, tell me\Nif I'm doing this wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,but it looks like if I use\Nthis little buddy in my deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I can search\Nnon-colored SIGNIs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! You sure can!\NI'm surprised you know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,For a newbie, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO chuckles sheepishly]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Guess we'll\Nhave to wait for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,to sell a single.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.86,Main,,0,0,0,,For now, you'll just have to get\Nbetter with the deck you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw this\None and charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,And now "Grow".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Hey, wait a minute.\NShow me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Level 2 again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you'd probably do better\Nif you strategize your growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] You have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Your gameplay is way\Ntoo straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What's wrong with\Nbeing straightforward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:15.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I'm, uh...\NI'm goin' to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOUNG YUZUKI] I'm gonna\Nmarry Kazuki one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[PRESCHOOL TEACHER]\NAww, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOUNG YUZUKI giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[PRESCHOOL GIRL]\NEwww, that's icky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, brothers and sisters can't\Nget married, you dumb baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to, then there's\Nsomething's wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\N"Too straightforward"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:22.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that? It just\Nmeans I'm honest, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,How exactly is that supposed\Nto be a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[cell phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,"So, who's gonna\Nbattle me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu-poo? Or Ru-ru?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I can't lose\Nto her. And I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait there, Tama, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA mewls sadly]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I feel really\Nsorry for that Hitoe girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny. But I... I feel like\NI have to battle Akira myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,even if I know\NI can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA groans sadly]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,No! I was just\Nthinking out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,so why would I get into\Na battle with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Do battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything\Nthat I'd even wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cept Grandma living\Na long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA meows sadly]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[school bells chiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[cell phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not hanging\Nwith Kazuki today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] No, he had\Nsomething to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[cell phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:07.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, Akira,\Nobsessed much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This last text says she's on\Nher way here now to find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, Ru. Let's\Nfind some place to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah, right.\NBut where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hey! Let's go in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they've got private\Nrooms where Akira won't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,be able to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never done\Nkaraoke before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, what songs\Nshould I even sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Figure it out when\Nwe get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, wait\Na minute, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta plan these\Nthings out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, like strategize\Nfor the big fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Strategize?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm! Yeah, 'cause--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah? Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] That's the girl\Nwho works at the card shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Momoka. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wow, they look pretty\Ncozy together, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Maybe they're\Non a da--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what?\NI don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's 'cause\Nyou don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,After that battle\Nthe other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,you saw what's at stake and how\Npeople like Hitoe can get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you taking this seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! Of course I am!\NDon't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.37,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I have no idea\Nwhat you're thinking, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well. That\Nmakes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But... I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That'd be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Please. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,For Midoriko's\Nsake, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Have a battle with\Nme! You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodness. Have you been hiding\Nfrom me, you naughty girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm just lucky I found ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hey, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Come on down here! This\Nbattle will be flippin' epic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,We are gonna have so much\Nfun! But I'll have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm gonna beat the\Nliving crap out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got some stress\NI need to work off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I shouldn't\Nwin. It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Piriluk! Go: Peek-a-Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hold on. Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We've even got\Na nice breeze, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"This Nonsensical Peace."
